snippet.title: Metal Eden -  Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
METAL EDEN, an adrenaline rush sci-fi FPS will be released on May 6, 2025 on PC, Xbox Series S/X and PlayStation 5! A game with unique gameplay mechanics such as core-ripping. It's time to unleash your hyperpower!

More info: https://www.Metaleden.com
